data.description: Adorable 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom home in Riley. This home has gorgeous hardwood floors throughout and was remodeled in 2016. Even more recently, it got a new furnace, water heater, front door, and kitchen backsplash. The living room is spacious, the kitchen is beautiful, there is the perfect spot for a dining table, and the bedrooms are a great size. The backyard is fully fenced and there is a detached garage in the back that has alley access. Come check this home out today! Call Lauren at 785-564-2693.
